  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB SUMMARY</strong></p><p>Responsible for the recruitment of CPD (Continuing Professional Development) Trainees for the company.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTIONS</strong></p><ul><li><p>To increase the CPD sales revenue for KLC International Institute.</p></li><li><p>Responsible for CPD sales activities. Build new customer base and provide excellent client management to maintain strong customer relationships.</p></li><li><p>Explore business opportunities, propose collaboration/partnership through trade fairs and conferences.</p></li><li><p>Generate regular reports and sales trends for regular reporting purposes.</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance of work flow processes, auditing, quality assurance and risk management procedures.</p></li><li><p>To perform any other duties as assigned.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min Diploma or Degree in Business Studies / Marketing / Mass Communications.</p></li><li><p>Min 2 years’ working experience, ideally working on consumer-facing, large scale products.</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication skills and strong interpersonal skills. </p></li><li><p>Good understanding of the adult training landscape in Singapore preferred.</p></li><li><p>Demonstrated ability to work in an ambiguous environment under tight deadlines.</p></li><li><p>Creative, motivated, entrepreneurial and achievement oriented.</p></li></ul>",
