    "description": "<p>KLC INTERNATIONAL INSTITUTE PTE. LTD. (KLCII)</p>\n<p>KLC International Institute, a member of the <a href=\"https://crestargroup.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://crestargroup.com/\"><u>Crestar Education Group (CEG)</u></a> with many regional businesses across Asia, is a human capital development organisation recognised for its innovation in professional training and lifelong learning.</p>\n<p>The institute is an acknowledged leader in adult education with a niche in early childhood teacher education. Over the last 35 years, KLCII has be able to reinvent itself to help its customers stay relevant in the changing business and education landscape. Currently, KLCII offers a suite of Business and Digital Transformation SkillsFuture Singapore (SSG)-funded, WSQ-approved courses to help enterprises reinvent themselves.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As part of its continuous evolution to contribute to communities across the region, KLCII is seeking to form a new team to facilitate its education and business outreach through technology.</p>",
